OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FThe Arbroath and Broughty Ferry
OL,8,Fconstituency is one of those rare
OL,9,Fbeasts which has city, town and rural
OL,10,Fvoters in one seat.
OL,12,FBut despite the diversity found in an
OL,13,Farea which includes the eastern tip of
OL,14,FDundee, the relative affluence of
OL,15,FBroughty Ferry, the relative
OL,16,Fdeprivation of Arbroath and the rural,
OL,17,Fagriculture wilds of Angus, candidates
OL,18,Fhave pinpointed a common issue ` the
OL,19,Fcost of living.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
