FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FThat phrase has been a common refrain
OL,8,Fsince the pandemic, when inflation
OL,9,Fspiked, along with fuel prices, and
OL,10,Fwages continued to stagnate.
OL,12,FBut with voters due to go to the polls
OL,13,Fin a by-election on June 18,
OL,14,Fcandidates have been vying to convince
OL,15,Fthem they will be the ones to take
OL,16,Faction.
OL,18,FThe contest was triggered by the
OL,19,Fresignation of Stephen Gethins after
OL,20,Fhis win at Holyrood in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FSpeaking to the Press Association in
OL,8,Fher campaign headquarters in Arbroath,
OL,9,FSNP candidate Lara Bird ` a lawyer,
OL,10,FPhD student and party adviser at
OL,11,FWestminster ` said the cost of living
OL,12,Fwas the key to the contest.
OL,14,F"This is a cost of living by-
OL,15,Felection," she said.
OL,17,F"What we're seeing and what we're
OL,18,Fhearing is that folk are genuinely
OL,19,Ffrustrated at the lack of action that
OL,20,FLabour is taking to tackle the cost of
OL,21,Fliving."
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@JO]yD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FA refusal to cut fuel duty and the
OL,8,Frise of the energy price cap, she
OL,9,Fsays, are coming up on the doors.
OL,11,F"In comparison, the SNP are taking
OL,12,Fgenuine action to do that, whether
OL,13,Fthat's capping the cost of essentials
OL,14,Fin the supermarkets, whether that is
OL,15,Fintroducing more childcare to help
OL,16,Ffolk who need extra childcare, and
OL,17,Fwhether that's taking action to cut
OL,18,Ffuel bills," she said.
OL,26,@sD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
