CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FConstituents "understand that it's the
OL,8,FSNP that are actually making those
OL,9,Fdecisions", she said.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Government has not yet
OL,12,Fset out how it will cap food prices `
OL,13,Fa policy which could face a
OL,14,Fsubstantial legal challenge or be
OL,15,Fblocked by Westminster ` while
OL,16,Flegislation to improve on the current
OL,17,F1,140 hours of free childcare has not
OL,18,Fyet been published.
OL,26,@oD@NOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
