PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FHeather Doran, a councillor and the
OL,8,FScottish Labour candidate, said she
OL,9,Fwanted to be a "local champion".
OL,11,F"People are worried about the impact
OL,12,Fof international (issues), such as
OL,13,FIran," she told PA.
OL,15,F"That's something that I would really
OL,16,Fraise for people as we're going
OL,17,Fthrough into the winter and how we can
OL,18,Fmake sure that our costs are
OL,19,Faffordable ` particularly on fuel `
OL,20,Fgoing forward."
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@_O]sD@AOUuD@FO]wD@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
