PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FBut both candidates risk their
OL,8,Fcampaigns being overshadowed by
OL,9,Fnational issues at a party level `
OL,10,Fwith the SNP still reeling from the
OL,11,Ffallout of former chief executive
OL,12,FPeter Murrell's admission of a
OL,13,F#400,000 embezzlement from party
OL,14,Fcoffers and the ongoing uncertainty
OL,15,Fover Sir Keir Starmer's premiership
OL,16,Fseemingly becoming an issue of
OL,17,Fconstant commentary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
