OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FMs Bird, however, said the issues
OL,8,Ffacing her party are far from the
OL,9,Fminds of Arbroath and Broughty Ferry
OL,10,Fvoters.
OL,12,F"No," the SNP candidate said when
OL,13,Fasked if the party's former chief
OL,14,Fexecutive ` and Nicola Sturgeon's ex-
OL,15,Fhusband's guilty plea was coming up on
OL,16,Fthe doors.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
