CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,F"What folk are interested in is the
OL,8,Fcost of living and they want to talk
OL,9,Fabout what it is that the SNP are
OL,10,Fdoing and what Labour are not doing to
OL,11,Ftackle the cost of living."
OL,13,FWhile her Labour opponent said people
OL,14,Fare looking for "some kind of change,
OL,15,Fparticularly in how things are
OL,16,Fcommunicated to them and how things
OL,17,Fare done".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@[O]vD@QOUyD@IO]
