OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FMs Doran refused to say if she
OL,8,Fsupports Sir Keir's leadership, but
OL,9,Fdid call for a "revamp" in the UK
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,FBill Reid is standing for Reform UK in
OL,13,Fthe hopes of winning the party's first
OL,14,Fconstituency north of the border.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
