OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,FHe too suggested that the cost-of-
OL,8,Fliving crisis was key to voters in the
OL,9,Farea, particularly rising fuel costs,
OL,10,Fwhich he said could be countered by
OL,11,Fdropping net zero policies and
OL,12,Fdrilling for oil and gas in the North
OL,13,FSea.
OL,15,FBut Mr Reid also suggested voters in
OL,16,FArbroath and Broughty Ferry could get
OL,17,Fin at the ground floor of a surge for
OL,18,Fhis party which could take Nigel
OL,19,FFarage into Downing Street.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
