PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,F"We're bringing common sense to
OL,8,Fpolitics," he told PA at the seafront
OL,9,Fin Broughty Ferry.
OL,11,F"We listen to people and we form our
OL,12,Fpolicies based on what people are
OL,13,Ftelling us.
OL,15,F"Hence, we're way, way way ahead in
OL,16,Fthe vote ` over 300 polls tell you
OL,17,Fthat people are listening to us and
OL,18,Fwe're listening to them.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@JO]sD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,F"That's why people, particularly in
OL,8,Fthis constituency, should vote Reform,
OL,9,Fbecause it's perfectly obvious `
OL,10,Funless we have some kind of nuclear
OL,11,Fexplosion ` that Reform are going to
OL,12,Fbe the next (government)
OL,14,F"The people here have got a chance on
OL,15,FJune 18 to be part of that.
OL,17,F"There's no point in voting for
OL,18,Fanybody else, you're going to be a
OL,19,Fbystander.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
