OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781576262
OL,3,CArbroath and Broughty Ferry: the
OL,4,Cdiverse seat suffering from the cost
OL,5,Cof living
OL,7,F"If they vote for Reform, they're
OL,8,Fgoing to formulate policy and they're
OL,9,Fgoing to get what they want in
OL,10,FParliament."
OL,12,FJack Cruickshanks of the Scottish
OL,13,FTories and Tanvir Ahmad of the Liberal
OL,14,FDemocrats are also running in the seat.
